{"word":"ἀθλητής","slug":"ἀθλητής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀθλητής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀθλέω'><el>ἀθλέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a prizefighter</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>athleta</el>: as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a>, <el>ἀθλ. ἵππος</el> a <i>race</i>-horse, <b><a href='S:Lysias'>Lys.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> rei, <i>practised in</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}